{"tid":1727193,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"全世界文宣集中戰線 - 二噁英","createTime":"2019-11-16T10:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T06:24:34.000Z","uid":49898,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3feff29442f8c061ae65644b07e60ea5d2dca4bf","tid":1727193,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:58:59.000Z","msg":"無論18區定海外文宣都好<br />\n集中火力<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連儂牆同我清乾淨<br />\n</span></span><br />\n今日開始不斷重複貼<br />\n一幅牆一式一樣重覆<br />\n或者超大型超清晰<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n二噁英對社區、對人類嘅影響<br />\n警隊亂放中国制有毒TG<br />\n政府一直都唔肯公開成分<br />\n有市民身體已有敏感反應<br />\n前線記者已出現中毒症狀<br />\n中毒後無法醫治<br />\n癌症<br />\n不育<br />\n生畸胎<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地之前搞咁多文宣<br />\n警暴 殺人 強姦 中共 政策 良知 民生<br />\n都好似無用<br />\n要歸邊嘅已一早歸邊<br />\n港豬藍屍根本無feel<br />\n覺得唔好搞到佢返工搵錢享受就咩都無所謂<br />\n<br />\n但二噁英問題係影響香港成個社區<br />\n佢地去邊都有機會直接接觸<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係會影響佢地身體 佢下一代健康同生育<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地要俾佢知枝針已經拮到埋肉喇<br />\n</span></span><br />\n化學教授指出問題極嚴重<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/179179469403545/posts/453229281998561?vh=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F179179469403545%2Fposts%2F453229281998561%3Fvh%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=fba06771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/179179469403545/posts/453229281998561?vh=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n立場匡哥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/503327553016621/posts/3072882642727753?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F503327553016621%2Fposts%2F3072882642727753%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=b7c0b667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/503327553016621/posts/3072882642727753?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n其他資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1306Nn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1306Nn.jpg&h=82ec1d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6obVbd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6obVbd3.jpg&h=a494013a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MCCECT6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMCCECT6.jpg&h=5ac9e899&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Goz34y7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGoz34y7.jpg&h=95acafa2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dct06Ns.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDct06Ns.jpg&h=e0d637ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGaiTst.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGaiTst.jpg&h=37a98b65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ONpO0O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ONpO0O.jpg&h=0a1a85e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uV434y9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuV434y9.jpg&h=9320bea0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BTUvKzb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBTUvKzb.png&h=6291750b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a7bb7ed5a1b3eb06659f1512aac9e2c9784d57d","tid":1727193,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:00:26.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n統一戰線<br />\n集中火力"},{"pid":"fb67f19f7ea230e9e082be53811d21b66f12aefd","tid":1727193,"uid":20306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:04:43.000Z","msg":"推 要出埋翻譯文宣"},{"pid":"4a3a11ebdf11a91e406c56e2a32ad7a33bef1686","tid":1727193,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:09:26.000Z","ms